WEBVTT

00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:13.930 line:80%
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:13.680 line:80%
My Lord!

00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:16.120 line:80%
My Lord!

00:00:17.030 --> 00:00:18.350 line:80%
My Lord!

00:00:18.690 --> 00:00:23.730 line:80%
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:23.050 line:80%
You must uphold justice for me!

00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:27.800 line:80%
My Lord!

00:00:28.770 --> 00:00:31.650 line:80%
You must uphold justice for me!

00:00:32.180 --> 00:00:34.010 line:80%
You jinx!

00:00:34.140 --> 00:00:36.730 line:80%
You actually killed your own uncle!

00:00:42.730 --> 00:00:43.830 line:80%
My... uncle?

00:00:45.170 --> 00:00:50.090 line:80%
I beg you, My Lord,
please uphold justice for us.

00:00:54.090 --> 00:00:56.210 line:80%
How did the plaintiff die?

00:00:56.770 --> 00:00:57.710 line:80%
My Lord,

00:00:57.760 --> 00:00:59.130 line:80%
when I found Fan Daniu,

00:00:59.130 --> 00:01:00.050 line:80%
he had already stopped breathing.

00:01:00.050 --> 00:01:01.320 line:80%
There were multiple knife wounds
on his body.

00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:03.220 line:80%
It looks like
he was hacked to death with a long knife.

00:01:03.220 --> 00:01:05.820 line:80%
My Lord, in my humble opinion,

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:08.380 line:80%
the killer was skilled with a knife.

00:01:09.300 --> 00:01:10.780 line:80%
It was her!

00:01:11.260 --> 00:01:12.940 line:80%
If it wasn't her,

00:01:12.970 --> 00:01:15.770 line:80%
who else
could be so good with a butcher knife?

00:01:15.800 --> 00:01:16.960 line:80%
I'll kill you!

00:01:16.980 --> 00:01:18.580 line:80%
I'll kill you!

00:01:18.850 --> 00:01:20.740 line:80%
Just for this house!

00:01:20.770 --> 00:01:22.040 line:80%
My Lord, I came to
the county government office

00:01:22.040 --> 00:01:23.320 line:80%
early in the morning.

00:01:23.500 --> 00:01:25.460 line:80%
The neighbors can all prove that!

00:01:25.480 --> 00:01:26.940 line:80%
Yes, we can prove that!

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:28.500 line:80%
-We can testify for Changyu!
-Last night,

00:01:28.500 --> 00:01:30.420 line:80%
-Changyu was at home!
-Yes!

00:01:30.420 --> 00:01:31.140 line:80%
And we came here

00:01:31.140 --> 00:01:32.740 line:80%
-with her in the morning!
-County Magistrate!

00:01:32.740 --> 00:01:33.940 line:80%
Changyu is innocent!

00:01:33.970 --> 00:01:34.690 line:80%
Silence!

00:01:35.220 --> 00:01:36.820 line:80%
I am investigating the case!

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:38.660 line:80%
My Lord,

00:01:39.380 --> 00:01:42.430 line:80%
even if she didn't do it herself,

00:01:42.450 --> 00:01:45.300 line:80%
she might have hired a killer.

00:01:45.690 --> 00:01:48.970 line:80%
How about we search her house first?

00:01:49.770 --> 00:01:50.559 line:80%
Right.

00:01:51.500 --> 00:01:52.089 line:80%
Guards!

00:01:52.690 --> 00:01:54.770 line:80%
Take Fan Changyu
into custody pending trial.

00:01:54.770 --> 00:01:55.250 line:80%
Yes.

00:01:55.250 --> 00:01:56.779 line:80%
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

00:01:56.779 --> 00:01:57.250 line:80%
Changyu!

00:01:57.250 --> 00:01:57.660 line:80%
Changyu!

00:01:57.660 --> 00:01:58.330 line:80%
It wasn't me!

00:01:58.330 --> 00:01:59.059 line:80%
Changyu!

00:01:59.170 --> 00:02:00.020 line:80%
Changyu!

00:02:00.660 --> 00:02:01.380 line:80%
Changyu!

00:02:01.380 --> 00:02:02.050 line:80%
Changyu!

00:02:02.530 --> 00:02:04.300 line:80%
Changyu, don't be afraid!

00:02:12.920 --> 00:02:15.080 line:80%
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:18.680 line:80%
Where is Constable Wang?

00:02:19.180 --> 00:02:20.100 line:80%
My Lord,

00:02:20.129 --> 00:02:23.660 line:80%
Constable Wang has already gone
to the Fan's house with his men.

00:02:34.890 --> 00:02:35.450 line:80%
Search!

00:02:37.500 --> 00:02:38.160 line:80%
Changning?

00:02:52.330 --> 00:02:52.930 line:80%
My Lord,

00:02:53.270 --> 00:02:54.290 line:80%
there's no one upstairs.

00:02:54.290 --> 00:02:55.480 line:80%
My Lord, there's no one in the backyard.

00:02:55.480 --> 00:02:56.610 line:80%
My Lord, no one.

00:02:58.750 --> 00:03:01.050 line:80%
It seems someone came
to the Fan family for revenge.

00:03:01.050 --> 00:03:01.860 line:80%
You two stay here.

00:03:01.860 --> 00:03:04.050 line:80%
The rest of you, follow me back to
the county government office to report.

00:03:04.050 --> 00:03:04.860 line:80%
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:04:32.230 --> 00:04:36.740 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:04:36.820 --> 00:04:39.320 line:80%
[Episode 7]

00:05:14.060 --> 00:05:14.890 line:80%
Don't blow it.

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:19.540 line:80%
My sister told me
to blow the whistle if I meet bad guys.

00:05:20.070 --> 00:05:21.750 line:80%
It's not the time yet.

00:05:22.110 --> 00:05:23.630 line:80%
Blowing the whistle now

00:05:24.410 --> 00:05:26.210 line:80%
will only attract more bad guys.

00:05:45.130 --> 00:05:45.930 line:80%
Mr. Wang,

00:05:47.450 --> 00:05:48.780 line:80%
I didn't kill Uncle.

00:05:49.520 --> 00:05:50.400 line:80%
I know.

00:05:51.230 --> 00:05:51.980 line:80%
Changyu,

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:55.420 line:80%
something happened at your home too.

00:06:01.290 --> 00:06:02.520 line:80%
When I got there,

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:05.520 line:80%
I saw three bodies on the ground.

00:06:09.770 --> 00:06:10.850 line:80%
Where is Changning?

00:06:10.850 --> 00:06:11.700 line:80%
Don't panic.

00:06:12.440 --> 00:06:15.240 line:80%
Those bodies
weren't your husband and Changning.

00:06:15.870 --> 00:06:17.410 line:80%
There was no one in the house,

00:06:17.410 --> 00:06:19.120 line:80%
but it had been ransacked.

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:22.530 line:80%
Maybe those people just took them away.

00:06:24.090 --> 00:06:26.830 line:80%
Someone reported movement
on the mountain outside the city.

00:06:26.830 --> 00:06:27.880 line:80%
Magistrate has sent people

00:06:27.880 --> 00:06:28.930 line:80%
-to search the mountain.
-I'll go find them.

00:06:28.930 --> 00:06:30.390 line:80%
You can't go out right now.

00:06:30.610 --> 00:06:33.770 line:80%
-The magistrate didn't let you go home.
-My parents are dead.

00:06:33.770 --> 00:06:36.150 line:80%
I only have this sister left, Mr. Wang.

00:06:36.380 --> 00:06:37.300 line:80%
I beg you.

00:06:58.410 --> 00:06:59.330 line:80%
Changyu.

00:07:00.980 --> 00:07:02.110 line:80%
You must be careful.

00:07:22.050 --> 00:07:22.900 line:80%
Changning,

00:07:23.170 --> 00:07:24.360 line:80%
count to 10.

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:40.820 line:80%
5.

00:07:41.540 --> 00:07:42.340 line:80%
6.

00:07:43.100 --> 00:07:43.900 line:80%
7.

00:07:44.420 --> 00:07:45.350 line:80%
8.

00:07:46.690 --> 00:07:47.490 line:80%
9.

00:07:53.130 --> 00:07:54.260 line:80%
Put your clothes on.

00:07:54.320 --> 00:07:55.570 line:80%
As long as you stay alive,

00:07:55.570 --> 00:07:57.300 line:80%
your sister will come save you.

00:08:16.860 --> 00:08:18.650 line:80%
Zheng...

00:08:19.050 --> 00:08:19.900 line:80%
Zheng.

00:08:20.340 --> 00:08:21.740 line:80%
Zheng!

00:08:23.320 --> 00:08:25.430 line:80%
Turn around. Don't look.

00:09:55.150 --> 00:09:56.720 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:09:56.740 --> 00:09:58.520 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:10:01.760 --> 00:10:03.990 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:10:20.130 --> 00:10:21.270 line:80%
I killed someone.

00:10:26.650 --> 00:10:28.290 line:80%
Sister!

00:10:37.280 --> 00:10:38.210 line:80%
Go, now!

00:10:39.580 --> 00:10:40.780 line:80%
Don't worry about me!

00:10:41.670 --> 00:10:44.280 line:80%
Take Changning and go!

00:10:48.770 --> 00:10:51.650 line:80%
Changyu! Zheng!

00:10:55.770 --> 00:10:56.940 line:80%
Good.

00:10:58.830 --> 00:11:01.460 line:80%
Now I can take care of
this bunch of trash.

00:12:03.810 --> 00:12:04.600 line:80%
How are you?

00:12:05.740 --> 00:12:07.200 line:80%
Didn't I tell you to leave?

00:12:07.340 --> 00:12:08.590 line:80%
Why did you come back?

00:12:08.900 --> 00:12:11.960 line:80%
I had to send Changning away
before coming back for you.

00:12:15.730 --> 00:12:16.680 line:80%
Hold on.

00:12:17.520 --> 00:12:18.950 line:80%
The official soldiers will be here soon.

00:12:18.950 --> 00:12:19.810 line:80%
Hold on!

00:13:07.820 --> 00:13:09.080 line:80%
Don't get distracted.

00:13:14.650 --> 00:13:16.020 line:80%
Who sent you?

00:13:16.150 --> 00:13:17.460 line:80%
What grudge do you hold
against the Fan family

00:13:17.460 --> 00:13:18.990 line:80%
that makes you want us dead?

00:13:39.820 --> 00:13:40.670 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:13:42.060 --> 00:13:43.130 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:13:52.290 --> 00:13:53.130 line:80%
Wake up.

00:13:53.980 --> 00:13:55.040 line:80%
Don't fall asleep.

00:13:55.560 --> 00:13:56.620 line:80%
We're almost home.

00:14:00.420 --> 00:14:01.700 line:80%
This is the second time

00:14:02.210 --> 00:14:04.010 line:80%
I'm carrying you out of the snow.

00:14:08.220 --> 00:14:11.230 line:80%
Other women find a man
to support the family.

00:14:12.810 --> 00:14:13.660 line:80%
Did I find a man

00:14:15.320 --> 00:14:17.450 line:80%
just to build up my physical strength?

00:14:20.970 --> 00:14:21.970 line:80%
Don't sleep.

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:23.800 line:80%
Hang in there.

00:14:26.780 --> 00:14:28.040 line:80%
You have to stay alive.

00:14:28.280 --> 00:14:29.810 line:80%
If anything happens to you,

00:14:30.070 --> 00:14:31.930 line:80%
I won't be able to repay this debt.

00:14:36.590 --> 00:14:37.970 line:80%
Get up. Don't sleep.

00:14:41.650 --> 00:14:43.450 line:80%
Thank you for saving Changning.

00:14:44.930 --> 00:14:45.960 line:80%
If she had died,

00:14:47.800 --> 00:14:49.010 line:80%
I really don't know

00:14:49.580 --> 00:14:51.310 line:80%
how I could have gone on living.

00:14:55.980 --> 00:14:57.150 line:80%
I owe you a lot.

00:14:58.690 --> 00:14:59.550 line:80%
Yan Zheng...

00:15:19.620 --> 00:15:20.530 line:80%
Yan Zheng...

00:15:22.140 --> 00:15:23.010 line:80%
Yan Zheng...

00:15:25.060 --> 00:15:26.040 line:80%
Wake up.

00:15:27.320 --> 00:15:28.280 line:80%
Don't sleep.

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:32.470 line:80%
Don't sleep, Yan Zheng.

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:34.360 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:15:35.980 --> 00:15:36.740 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:15:37.980 --> 00:15:38.740 line:80%
Don't sleep.

00:15:40.940 --> 00:15:41.870 line:80%
Don't sleep...

00:15:48.740 --> 00:15:51.040 line:80%
Sister!

00:16:04.130 --> 00:16:05.980 line:80%
Changyu! Zheng!

00:16:06.060 --> 00:16:08.050 line:80%
Wake up!

00:16:08.100 --> 00:16:09.710 line:80%
Changyu! Zheng!

00:16:10.340 --> 00:16:11.100 line:80%
Let's go home.

00:16:11.100 --> 00:16:13.130 line:80%
Changyu! Changyu!

00:16:14.070 --> 00:16:14.780 line:80%
Changyu!

00:16:15.800 --> 00:16:16.660 line:80%
Help!

00:16:31.610 --> 00:16:32.490 line:80%
Zheng.

00:16:33.660 --> 00:16:36.600 line:80%
Your father is a great hero
with unyielding integrity.

00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:37.880 line:80%
In the future, you must also

00:16:37.880 --> 00:16:39.830 line:80%
become a man like him.

00:16:44.730 --> 00:16:46.970 line:80%
Zheng, eat more.

00:16:47.100 --> 00:16:48.820 line:80%
-Dad, here you are.
-Eat more.

00:16:48.960 --> 00:16:50.960 line:80%
You have to eat if you want strength.

00:16:51.740 --> 00:16:53.160 line:80%
Zheng, eat well,

00:16:53.250 --> 00:16:55.850 line:80%
so you can grow up
to be as strong as your father.

00:17:00.320 --> 00:17:01.830 line:80%
Xie Linshan...

00:17:02.620 --> 00:17:04.360 line:80%
Xie Linshan!

00:17:06.460 --> 00:17:08.399 line:80%
Xie Linshan...

00:17:08.960 --> 00:17:09.600 line:80%
Mother!

00:17:20.470 --> 00:17:22.899 line:80%
Why did you break your promise?

00:17:22.930 --> 00:17:25.960 line:80%
You said you'd come back
and paint my eyebrows.

00:17:30.270 --> 00:17:31.110 line:80%
Mother!

00:17:43.950 --> 00:17:44.810 line:80%
Zheng,

00:17:45.420 --> 00:17:47.750 line:80%
I made these osmanthus cakes myself.

00:17:47.900 --> 00:17:48.900 line:80%
They're so sweet.

00:17:49.180 --> 00:17:50.530 line:80%
Take them outside to eat.

00:17:50.530 --> 00:17:51.220 line:80%
Okay.

00:17:52.480 --> 00:17:53.650 line:80%
When you come back,

00:17:53.670 --> 00:17:55.930 line:80%
pick some more osmanthus flowers for me.

00:17:56.230 --> 00:17:58.230 line:80%
I'll make you more osmanthus cakes.

00:17:58.970 --> 00:18:01.610 line:80%
Zheng, remember,

00:18:02.090 --> 00:18:05.250 line:80%
osmanthus cake is my favorite.

00:18:14.460 --> 00:18:16.130 line:80%
No! Don't!

00:18:16.220 --> 00:18:18.480 line:80%
Don't eat the osmanthus cakes! Don't go!

00:18:25.700 --> 00:18:26.250 line:80%
Mother!

00:18:29.770 --> 00:18:30.420 line:80%
Mother!

00:18:31.530 --> 00:18:32.140 line:80%
Mother!

00:18:32.940 --> 00:18:33.620 line:80%
Mother!

00:18:38.010 --> 00:18:38.470 line:80%
Mother!

00:19:13.550 --> 00:19:14.310 line:80%
Mother!

00:19:34.250 --> 00:19:35.220 line:80%
Zheng.

00:19:37.340 --> 00:19:38.940 line:80%
Do not miss me.

00:19:41.560 --> 00:19:43.690 line:80%
I can't be with you as you grow up.

00:20:04.890 --> 00:20:08.880 line:80%
Mother, don't leave me behind.

00:20:24.220 --> 00:20:26.030 line:80%
I just wanted to feed you medicine.

00:20:26.030 --> 00:20:28.430 line:80%
Why did you act like
I was trying to kill you?

00:20:30.810 --> 00:20:31.720 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:20:35.010 --> 00:20:35.570 line:80%
Here.

00:20:35.570 --> 00:20:36.570 line:80%
I'll do it myself.

00:20:39.740 --> 00:20:40.940 line:80%
This hand of yours...

00:20:41.260 --> 00:20:43.310 line:80%
has two deep cuts from a sword.

00:20:44.220 --> 00:20:46.250 line:80%
On this hand, the web between
your thumb and forefinger is torn.

00:20:46.250 --> 00:20:47.140 line:80%
The doctor said

00:20:47.630 --> 00:20:50.430 line:80%
you shouldn't use force
with either of your hands.

00:21:05.980 --> 00:21:07.970 line:80%
No need. I don't like sweets.

00:21:08.140 --> 00:21:10.540 line:80%
Don't worry. It's not osmanthus flavored.

00:21:11.220 --> 00:21:12.850 line:80%
I heard you shouting just now

00:21:13.090 --> 00:21:15.820 line:80%
about not wanting
to eat osmanthus or something.

00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:17.530 line:80%
I knew you wouldn't like it.

00:21:18.620 --> 00:21:20.620 line:80%
This is dried tangerine peel candy.

00:21:23.120 --> 00:21:24.030 line:80%
The doctor said

00:21:24.870 --> 00:21:27.270 line:80%
your injuries are quite serious this time.

00:21:27.420 --> 00:21:30.350 line:80%
He repeatedly said
you should rest and recover well.

00:21:31.530 --> 00:21:33.620 line:80%
Anyway, until you're healed,

00:21:33.650 --> 00:21:35.330 line:80%
you can't lift heavy objects.

00:21:39.830 --> 00:21:42.530 line:80%
Our home has been sealed
by the county government office.

00:21:42.530 --> 00:21:43.860 line:80%
We can't go back for now.

00:21:44.090 --> 00:21:46.550 line:80%
So we'll just squeeze in
at Mr. Zhao's place.

00:21:46.610 --> 00:21:49.470 line:80%
Just focus on recovering
in the attic and rest easy.

00:21:50.440 --> 00:21:53.200 line:80%
Changyu, Yan Zheng, dinner is ready.

00:21:54.140 --> 00:21:54.810 line:80%
Okay.

00:21:57.770 --> 00:21:58.830 line:80%
I'll go down first.

00:21:59.090 --> 00:22:00.620 line:80%
I'll bring you food in a bit.

00:22:14.090 --> 00:22:16.150 line:80%
Thank you for protecting Changning.

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:05.240 line:80%
Who sent you?

00:23:05.270 --> 00:23:06.470 line:80%
What grudge do you hold
against the Fan family

00:23:06.470 --> 00:23:08.000 line:80%
that makes you want us dead?

00:23:16.740 --> 00:23:18.270 line:80%
The Iron Suicide Warriors?

00:23:18.800 --> 00:23:21.600 line:80%
The Wei family's lackeys
have noticed this place,

00:23:22.590 --> 00:23:24.690 line:80%
but they weren't coming for me.

00:23:27.530 --> 00:23:32.190 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:23:29.850 --> 00:23:32.460 line:80%
Dry weather!

00:23:32.810 --> 00:23:34.530 line:80%
Beware of fire!

00:23:34.530 --> 00:23:36.140 line:80%
Here, the brazier.

00:23:39.640 --> 00:23:40.530 line:80%
Are you cold or what?

00:23:40.530 --> 00:23:41.460 line:80%
What's going on?

00:23:41.490 --> 00:23:42.940 line:80%
Why are your hands shaking so badly?

00:23:42.940 --> 00:23:44.500 line:80%
I... I don't know.

00:23:44.900 --> 00:23:47.760 line:80%
It's been like this
since I came back from the woods.

00:23:48.410 --> 00:23:49.200 line:80%
You...

00:23:49.220 --> 00:23:51.480 line:80%
I probably just caught a cold. It's fine.

00:23:56.810 --> 00:23:57.660 line:80%
You're awake?

00:24:06.660 --> 00:24:08.390 line:80%
Go to sleep. I'll stay with you.

00:24:27.800 --> 00:24:30.000 line:80%
You woke up sweating profusely at noon.

00:24:31.520 --> 00:24:33.850 line:80%
Was it a nightmare because of the killing?

00:24:43.650 --> 00:24:44.300 line:80%
Yes.

00:24:45.570 --> 00:24:47.830 line:80%
It was my first time killing someone too.

00:24:49.400 --> 00:24:50.530 line:80%
Were you scared?

00:24:55.060 --> 00:24:56.030 line:80%
Actually...

00:24:58.560 --> 00:24:59.770 line:80%
you were scared too.

00:25:04.060 --> 00:25:05.390 line:80%
I'm not scared anymore.

00:25:08.000 --> 00:25:10.260 line:80%
It's just that my hands are shaking a bit.

00:25:16.510 --> 00:25:18.920 line:80%
Actually,
you don't need to be afraid either.

00:25:18.920 --> 00:25:21.180 line:80%
Do something else over the next few days,

00:25:21.180 --> 00:25:22.440 line:80%
like butchering pigs.

00:25:22.660 --> 00:25:24.090 line:80%
You don't know how to butcher pigs,
do you?

00:25:24.090 --> 00:25:25.290 line:80%
I'll teach you later.

00:25:26.550 --> 00:25:27.550 line:80%
That way,

00:25:28.350 --> 00:25:32.080 line:80%
you'll have a livelihood if you
stop escorting goods in the future.

00:25:42.220 --> 00:25:43.280 line:80%
Come sit over here.

00:25:44.380 --> 00:25:45.240 line:80%
It's warm here.

00:25:54.090 --> 00:25:55.290 line:80%
Old people say

00:25:55.570 --> 00:25:57.700 line:80%
butchers have an aura of death

00:25:58.140 --> 00:25:59.800 line:80%
that keeps evil spirits away.

00:26:00.380 --> 00:26:01.440 line:80%
If I watch over you,

00:26:01.810 --> 00:26:03.810 line:80%
you won't have nightmares anymore.

00:26:12.770 --> 00:26:15.040 line:80%
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

00:26:14.220 --> 00:26:14.980 line:80%
Thank you.

00:26:16.040 --> 00:26:17.380 line:80%
♪ With very pale colors ♪

00:26:18.160 --> 00:26:21.000 line:80%
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

00:26:21.460 --> 00:26:24.040 line:80%
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

00:26:24.700 --> 00:26:26.270 line:80%
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

00:26:26.860 --> 00:26:31.170 line:80%
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

00:26:34.390 --> 00:26:37.100 line:80%
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

00:26:37.730 --> 00:26:39.380 line:80%
♪ The light shines ♪

00:26:39.960 --> 00:26:42.930 line:80%
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

00:26:43.150 --> 00:26:45.830 line:80%
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

00:26:46.380 --> 00:26:48.200 line:80%
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

00:26:48.570 --> 00:26:53.560 line:80%
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

00:26:55.980 --> 00:26:57.260 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:26:57.280 --> 00:26:59.890 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

00:27:00.440 --> 00:27:01.570 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

00:27:01.590 --> 00:27:03.800 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

00:27:04.520 --> 00:27:08.560 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:27:08.910 --> 00:27:12.680 line:80%
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

00:27:13.290 --> 00:27:14.400 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

00:27:14.420 --> 00:27:16.970 line:80%
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

00:27:18.030 --> 00:27:19.140 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

00:27:19.160 --> 00:27:21.590 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

00:27:22.140 --> 00:27:26.250 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:27:26.510 --> 00:27:34.940 line:80%
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

00:27:41.660 --> 00:27:43.660 line:80%
Changning, go fetch me some water.

00:28:17.520 --> 00:28:18.510 line:80%
Just put it here.

00:28:30.890 --> 00:28:34.150 line:80%
Mr. Wang, has the verdict
come down from the county office?

00:28:38.610 --> 00:28:39.570 line:80%
Constable Wang, you're here.

00:28:39.570 --> 00:28:40.500 line:80%
Constable Wang.

00:28:46.250 --> 00:28:49.620 line:80%
[Arrest Warrant]

00:28:48.770 --> 00:28:50.300 line:80%
By order of the Magistrate:

00:28:50.620 --> 00:28:52.280 line:80%
Yan Zheng, husband of Fan Changyu,

00:28:52.280 --> 00:28:53.790 line:80%
[Arrest Warrant]

00:28:52.530 --> 00:28:53.790 line:80%
is suspected of murder

00:28:55.140 --> 00:28:57.140 line:80%
and is to be arrested to await trial.

00:29:02.270 --> 00:29:06.540 line:80%
[Qingping County Government Office]

00:29:26.730 --> 00:29:29.650 line:80%
Fan Changyu,
Fan Daniu's case isn't closed yet.

00:29:29.740 --> 00:29:31.380 line:80%
As a key suspect,

00:29:31.460 --> 00:29:33.850 line:80%
you should be in prison awaiting trial,

00:29:34.070 --> 00:29:36.330 line:80%
yet you dared to escape during the chaos.

00:29:36.420 --> 00:29:39.110 line:80%
I haven't held you accountable yet,

00:29:39.140 --> 00:29:40.940 line:80%
and you actually came before me?

00:29:41.400 --> 00:29:43.600 line:80%
Guards. Arrest her as well.

00:29:44.410 --> 00:29:45.820 line:80%
My wife has witnesses.

00:29:46.810 --> 00:29:48.330 line:80%
She has nothing to do
with the Fan Daniu case.

00:29:48.290 --> 00:29:52.650 line:80%
[Government]

00:29:48.790 --> 00:29:49.790 line:80%
May I ask, My Lord,

00:29:50.070 --> 00:29:51.540 line:80%
during your investigation,

00:29:51.540 --> 00:29:53.470 line:80%
have you found any solid evidence?

00:29:56.530 --> 00:29:58.530 line:80%
Matrilocal husband of Fan Changyu,

00:29:58.660 --> 00:30:00.180 line:80%
when you married into the Fan family,

00:30:00.180 --> 00:30:02.380 line:80%
you didn't report to the county office.

00:30:03.090 --> 00:30:04.910 line:80%
Since you are from another place,

00:30:04.910 --> 00:30:08.180 line:80%
do you have a travel permit
to prove your identity?

00:30:08.330 --> 00:30:09.790 line:80%
We have the travel permit.

00:30:12.330 --> 00:30:13.110 line:80%
It's here.

00:30:12.930 --> 00:30:15.470 line:80%
[Government]

00:30:19.940 --> 00:30:21.850 line:80%
[Applicant:
Fan Changyu, Xigu Lane, Lin'an Town]

00:30:23.470 --> 00:30:24.370 line:80%
I knew it.

00:30:26.610 --> 00:30:33.640 line:80%
[Travel Permit]

00:30:26.760 --> 00:30:30.130 line:80%
This travel permit
was reissued recently, wasn't it?

00:30:30.460 --> 00:30:32.580 line:80%
There is no document
from your place of origin.

00:30:32.580 --> 00:30:33.620 line:80%
Is that correct?

00:30:33.870 --> 00:30:35.800 line:80%
I encountered bandits on the road,

00:30:36.080 --> 00:30:37.320 line:80%
and lost the document
from my place of origin.

00:30:37.170 --> 00:30:39.320 line:80%
[Travel Permit]

00:30:38.380 --> 00:30:40.920 line:80%
I have asked someone
to go back to reissue it.

00:30:41.190 --> 00:30:42.390 line:80%
It will arrive later.

00:30:44.280 --> 00:30:45.860 line:80%
In that case,

00:30:46.280 --> 00:30:49.010 line:80%
your travel permit is not in order.

00:30:53.810 --> 00:30:54.890 line:80%
My Lord,

00:30:55.090 --> 00:30:56.650 line:80%
Yan Zheng has married into the Fan family,

00:30:56.650 --> 00:30:58.360 line:80%
which means he has a local guarantor.

00:30:58.360 --> 00:30:59.490 line:80%
According
to the Legal Code of Great Yin...

00:30:59.490 --> 00:31:00.890 line:80%
Shut up, Constable Wang.

00:31:07.180 --> 00:31:08.510 line:80%
You audacious peasant!

00:31:08.950 --> 00:31:11.480 line:80%
How dare you
pose as a resident of this county?

00:31:12.060 --> 00:31:16.080 line:80%
I suspect you are a bandit
from Qingfeng Stronghold,

00:31:16.730 --> 00:31:19.670 line:80%
working in collusion
to bring villains here

00:31:20.140 --> 00:31:22.120 line:80%
and ruin the peace of Lin'an.

00:31:22.590 --> 00:31:24.830 line:80%
No! He's wrongly accused, My Lord!

00:31:24.940 --> 00:31:26.480 line:80%
We are the victims!

00:31:26.510 --> 00:31:28.840 line:80%
My sister and husband were nearly killed!

00:31:29.200 --> 00:31:31.180 line:80%
How can you
not distinguish right from wrong?

00:31:31.180 --> 00:31:31.940 line:80%
How dare you!

00:31:32.160 --> 00:31:35.230 line:80%
You dare accuse our County Magistrate?

00:31:35.250 --> 00:31:39.130 line:80%
You claim you were nearly killed,

00:31:39.510 --> 00:31:41.580 line:80%
but perhaps
it was an uneven split of the loot,

00:31:41.580 --> 00:31:43.750 line:80%
leading to infighting. Who knows?

00:31:54.920 --> 00:31:56.320 line:80%
Just wait a few more days.

00:31:56.330 --> 00:31:57.850 line:80%
Once the travel permit arrives,

00:31:57.850 --> 00:31:59.380 line:80%
the truth will be revealed.

00:32:01.490 --> 00:32:04.380 line:80%
Why would I wait for you to judge a case?

00:32:04.570 --> 00:32:05.950 line:80%
You audacious refugee!

00:32:05.970 --> 00:32:08.840 line:80%
You are full of lies and deceiving me.

00:32:08.870 --> 00:32:09.550 line:80%
Guards!

00:32:09.880 --> 00:32:11.490 line:80%
Give him 20 heavy lashes.

00:32:11.810 --> 00:32:14.380 line:80%
Bring the confession and make him sign it.

00:32:15.180 --> 00:32:15.900 line:80%
Stop!

00:32:16.770 --> 00:32:18.300 line:80%
As a court official,

00:32:18.370 --> 00:32:20.570 line:80%
you want to torture me into confessing?

00:32:20.740 --> 00:32:22.800 line:80%
How dare you slander me!

00:32:23.510 --> 00:32:24.470 line:80%
Beat him!

00:32:24.510 --> 00:32:25.340 line:80%
Beat him hard!

00:32:25.420 --> 00:32:27.560 line:80%
My Lord, he is injured!

00:32:27.620 --> 00:32:30.050 line:80%
Beat me instead, My Lord!

00:32:30.460 --> 00:32:33.050 line:80%
Make sure he confesses
his connection to the bandits!

00:32:33.050 --> 00:32:33.740 line:80%
Beat him!

00:32:37.410 --> 00:32:38.570 line:80%
My Lord!

00:33:00.660 --> 00:33:01.590 line:80%
Are you alright?

00:33:04.140 --> 00:33:04.770 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:33:05.090 --> 00:33:06.050 line:80%
Rebellion! This is rebellion!

00:33:06.050 --> 00:33:08.050 line:80%
What do you think this courtroom is?

00:33:08.220 --> 00:33:09.290 line:80%
My Lord!

00:33:09.290 --> 00:33:10.730 line:80%
This girl is innocent!

00:33:10.810 --> 00:33:13.090 line:80%
Have pity on this orphan!

00:33:13.090 --> 00:33:13.810 line:80%
Yes!

00:33:13.810 --> 00:33:15.050 line:80%
Have pity on them!

00:33:15.650 --> 00:33:19.010 line:80%
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:33:16.630 --> 00:33:17.880 line:80%
Relying on you position,

00:33:17.880 --> 00:33:18.810 line:80%
you're bullying an orphan girl!

00:33:18.810 --> 00:33:19.700 line:80%
That's right!

00:33:19.730 --> 00:33:21.730 line:80%
How can you bully someone like this?

00:33:22.120 --> 00:33:23.660 line:80%
Injustice, My Lord!

00:33:23.740 --> 00:33:24.840 line:80%
Injustice!

00:33:25.290 --> 00:33:26.330 line:80%
Please!

00:33:26.330 --> 00:33:27.330 line:80%
My Lord!

00:33:27.810 --> 00:33:28.800 line:80%
My Lord,

00:33:28.980 --> 00:33:30.410 line:80%
why don't we wait a few more days

00:33:30.410 --> 00:33:32.210 line:80%
to avoid a wrongful conviction?

00:33:33.320 --> 00:33:35.620 line:80%
My Lord, public opinion
is a powerful thing.

00:33:35.620 --> 00:33:37.220 line:80%
Do not provoke public anger.

00:33:40.050 --> 00:33:40.810 line:80%
Silence!

00:33:42.020 --> 00:33:45.270 line:80%
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:33:42.400 --> 00:33:43.850 line:80%
One case at a time.

00:33:44.660 --> 00:33:47.460 line:80%
Fan Changyu,
as a suspect in the Fan Daniu case,

00:33:47.560 --> 00:33:49.360 line:80%
you shouldn't even be here.

00:33:50.300 --> 00:33:53.100 line:80%
Constable Wang,
take her back to the prison first.

00:33:55.770 --> 00:33:56.340 line:80%
Yes.

00:34:01.290 --> 00:34:03.480 line:80%
Changyu, come with me.

00:34:08.249 --> 00:34:08.890 line:80%
It's fine.

00:34:21.420 --> 00:34:24.530 line:80%
[Government]

00:34:50.660 --> 00:34:53.590 line:80%
My Lord,
it's safer to lock them in prison.

00:34:54.060 --> 00:34:57.020 line:80%
Just make sure
some evidence is planted in the end.

00:35:03.970 --> 00:35:05.020 line:80%
I'll give you one last...

00:35:05.020 --> 00:35:07.220 line:80%
I'll give you one last chance.

00:35:17.750 --> 00:35:19.800 line:80%
Preposterous! Seize him!

00:35:32.190 --> 00:35:33.840 line:80%
I explained the law to you,

00:35:34.500 --> 00:35:36.200 line:80%
but you are bent on framing me.

00:35:37.390 --> 00:35:38.720 line:80%
Since that's the case,

00:35:39.970 --> 00:35:41.610 line:80%
we'll do it my way!

00:35:41.640 --> 00:35:43.330 line:80%
Wh-What do you want?

00:35:43.840 --> 00:35:45.570 line:80%
You're just a mere commoner.

00:35:45.600 --> 00:35:46.600 line:80%
You actually dare

00:35:46.670 --> 00:35:48.880 line:80%
to harm our County Magistrate?

00:35:49.130 --> 00:35:51.040 line:80%
You're just a magistrate.

00:35:52.540 --> 00:35:54.400 line:80%
You actually dare to rebel?

00:35:54.530 --> 00:35:55.090 line:80%
What...

00:35:55.270 --> 00:35:56.510 line:80%
What are you saying?

00:35:56.530 --> 00:35:58.210 line:80%
You are the one rebelling!

00:35:58.800 --> 00:36:01.210 line:80%
Sir, don't be impulsive.

00:36:14.230 --> 00:36:15.420 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:36:26.450 --> 00:36:27.540 line:80%
Magistrate,

00:36:28.020 --> 00:36:29.750 line:80%
this joke has gone a bit too far.

00:36:30.450 --> 00:36:32.720 line:80%
[Travel Permit]

00:36:31.290 --> 00:36:33.220 line:80%
Yan Zheng's travel permit is here.

00:36:35.900 --> 00:36:39.230 line:80%
[Travel Permit]

00:36:38.140 --> 00:36:39.740 line:80%
You have internal injuries?

00:36:45.680 --> 00:36:46.800 line:80%
Did you miss me?

00:36:46.840 --> 00:36:47.660 line:80%
At this very moment,

00:36:47.660 --> 00:36:48.640 line:80%
do I look

00:36:48.640 --> 00:36:50.110 line:80%
-especially pleasing to your eyes?
-If you had come later,

00:36:50.110 --> 00:36:51.730 line:80%
I would have smashed this place.

00:36:51.730 --> 00:36:54.190 line:80%
Come on, let's avoid trouble.
Leave it to me.

00:36:55.610 --> 00:36:56.570 line:80%
My Lord,

00:36:57.060 --> 00:36:59.120 line:80%
Yan Zheng comes from Luyuan Academy.

00:36:59.290 --> 00:37:01.010 line:80%
The travel permit and documents are here.

00:36:59.770 --> 00:37:02.680 line:80%
[Travel Permit]

00:37:01.180 --> 00:37:02.620 line:80%
May we speak in private?

00:37:04.330 --> 00:37:05.580 line:80%
Luyuan Academy?

00:37:07.180 --> 00:37:07.780 line:80%
Please.

00:37:08.340 --> 00:37:11.460 line:80%
[Government]

00:37:15.000 --> 00:37:20.000 line:80%
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:37:21.140 --> 00:37:21.770 line:80%
This way.

00:37:28.230 --> 00:37:29.740 line:80%
Everything is settled. Don't worry.

00:37:29.740 --> 00:37:30.550 line:80%
My Lord,

00:37:30.570 --> 00:37:32.020 line:80%
he is merely a student.

00:37:32.020 --> 00:37:33.480 line:80%
Is such respect necessary?

00:37:33.480 --> 00:37:34.410 line:80%
What do you know?

00:37:34.410 --> 00:37:36.930 line:80%
Luyuan Academy is the premier
literary institution in the realm.

00:37:36.930 --> 00:37:38.480 line:80%
Those young men of noble families

00:37:38.480 --> 00:37:40.610 line:80%
are not people a lowly magistrate
like me can afford to offend.

00:37:40.610 --> 00:37:42.380 line:80%
It is inconvenient for us
to reveal our identities.

00:37:42.380 --> 00:37:44.120 line:80%
It is better to avoid unnecessary trouble.

00:37:44.120 --> 00:37:45.850 line:80%
Is he even fit to be an official?

00:37:46.920 --> 00:37:48.600 line:80%
He is merely useless trash.

00:37:48.630 --> 00:37:50.220 line:80%
Do with him as you like later.

00:37:50.220 --> 00:37:51.410 line:80%
We're at a disadvantage right now.

00:37:51.410 --> 00:37:53.140 line:80%
Let's get out of trouble first.

00:38:04.850 --> 00:38:06.850 line:80%
I have ascertained the truth.

00:38:07.020 --> 00:38:09.500 line:80%
Listen to the verdict.

00:38:11.540 --> 00:38:15.060 line:80%
Summon the Fan family's
eldest daughter-in-law, Mi.

00:38:22.140 --> 00:38:25.240 line:80%
Yan Zheng is an innocent commoner.

00:38:25.560 --> 00:38:29.790 line:80%
Uh... he was forced to kill some bandits
to protect his family.

00:38:30.370 --> 00:38:32.570 line:80%
He has nothing to do
with Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:38:32.570 --> 00:38:35.490 line:80%
Therefore, he is acquitted.

00:38:36.440 --> 00:38:37.310 line:80%
Great!

00:38:37.340 --> 00:38:38.530 line:80%
What about Fan Changyu?

00:38:38.530 --> 00:38:40.650 line:80%
Yes! What about Fan Changyu?

00:38:41.650 --> 00:38:44.140 line:80%
Well, there is currently
no evidence proving

00:38:44.140 --> 00:38:46.140 line:80%
that Fan Changyu is the real murderer.

00:38:46.140 --> 00:38:48.120 line:80%
She'll be released as well.

00:38:50.090 --> 00:38:52.500 line:80%
My Lord!

00:38:52.660 --> 00:38:55.570 line:80%
You must uphold justice for me!

00:38:55.850 --> 00:38:58.340 line:80%
Fan Daniu died such an unjust death!

00:38:58.850 --> 00:38:59.500 line:80%
Silence!

00:39:00.860 --> 00:39:03.510 line:80%
It is all your fault,
you unreasonable shrew!

00:39:03.540 --> 00:39:04.520 line:80%
Making such a racket.

00:39:04.520 --> 00:39:05.450 line:80%
What a disgrace!

00:39:05.850 --> 00:39:07.060 line:80%
As for the truth,

00:39:07.060 --> 00:39:08.500 line:80%
I have my own judgment.

00:39:08.530 --> 00:39:10.330 line:80%
If you dare to cause more trouble,

00:39:10.330 --> 00:39:12.260 line:80%
you will all be severely punished.

00:39:14.230 --> 00:39:15.360 line:80%
Court is dismissed!

00:39:21.410 --> 00:39:22.890 line:80%
-Yan Zheng!
-Yan Zheng!

00:39:27.290 --> 00:39:28.770 line:80%
Luckily I arrived early.

00:39:28.800 --> 00:39:31.260 line:80%
Otherwise,
you really would have died here.

00:39:34.190 --> 00:39:34.910 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:39:35.250 --> 00:39:35.850 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:39:38.130 --> 00:39:39.790 line:80%
Take good care of Fan Changyu.

00:39:40.200 --> 00:39:41.010 line:80%
Of course.

00:39:44.280 --> 00:39:45.310 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:39:45.420 --> 00:39:46.610 line:80%
Who is Fan Changyu?